<a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> </bibl> l.c. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6129.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">μετρητής</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0566.tlg001:374\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Theopomp.Hist.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">374</biblScope></bibl>. (The later form was <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφορεύς,</foreign> q.v.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}